{"tid":1281434,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"震驚！616游行民陣果千二萬去咗邊！","createTime":"2019-07-03T09:38:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T15:56:59.000Z","uid":243691,"like":15,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"73858d43e304c74d39c47764f3729b635c2414de","tid":1281434,"uid":243691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:38:40.000Z","msg":"唔係分化 <br />\n政府開始大搜捕 以好多唔合理罪名捉人<br />\n而且今日只係開始 之後一定陸續有黎<br />\n希望民陣可以將果千二萬透明化<br />\n幫612義士之餘 仲要拎黎幫因71被搜捕既義士<br />\n但係去到今日都未知果千二萬下落<br />\n希望民陣可以出黎講兩句<br />\n等市民大眾同被捕既人一個安心 令佢地唔洗煩惱錢銀既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b6952b7efb1b7f9203f3223184c0a3b44484348","tid":1281434,"uid":243691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:38:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9563c7b3b23654458c866ff99bd68514d3608b9e","tid":1281434,"uid":243691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:39:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6b3b0728b3ca27483ca4bb1df95d2001b79330a","tid":1281434,"uid":243691,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:40:04.000Z","msg":"民陣今次幫到義士既 選票自然歸佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f85cc015cc9571ebdbbb15a9ce2a530c840ad82","tid":1281434,"uid":243691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:40:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d833adbf05a26b542d10c3b7f555f72214c1f32e","tid":1281434,"uid":243691,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:41:23.000Z","msg":"負皮班人係咪想義士死？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eef557707546d8e1c9edaa5e45e2542ff2bba1d","tid":1281434,"uid":243691,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":